TextChange: Six years ago today, I came to a crossroads in my life and I decided I must make some changes. I was going through a most difficult time in my life, plus I had let myself get in terrible physical, mental, and spiritual shape. There was a point on that August 1st, 2015 that I really didn't want to continue on with life any more, but I did decide to press on. So on August 2, 2015 I vowed to make some changes and make my health and mental state a top priority. \nI've done well in keeping all the promises I made to myself. I've continued to go to church most every week, and I'm still doing my best to diet and maintain my weight. At my best weight about four years ago, I lost 127 pounds.
